text: Julia Sude (born 2 September 1987 in Gießen) is a German beach volleyball player. ==Professional career== Since 2015 her teammate has been Chantal Laboureur. ==World tour 2016== At the 2016 Grand Slam at Long Beach, California, In semi final action (Aug 27, 2016) Julia Sude and Laboureur lost to Kerri Walsh Jennings and April Ross of United States straight sets (21 - 17, 21 - 16). Bronze medal match (Germany vs Germany) the pair won in straight sets (21-16, 21-17) against Katrin Holtwick and Ilka Semmler. The pair competed at the Toronto World Tour finals in Sept. 2016 Team Details placing 1st in Pool D and advance to Quarter Finals. == References == ==External links== * Julia Sude at FIVB Category:German women's beach volleyball players Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Universiade bronze medalists for Germany Category:Universiade medalists in beach volleyball Category:Medalists at the 2013 Summer Universiade
